<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.2.9">
<l>kūvikūvik koṭuviṉai tūṟṟu ṇiṉṟu</l>
<l>pāviyēṉ palakālam vaḻitikait talamarkiṉṟēṉ</l>
<l>mēviyaṉ ṟānirai kāttava ṉulakamellān</l>
<l>tāviya vammāṉai yeṅkiṉit talaippeyvaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Calling, calling, standing inside the thicket of cruel karma,</l>
<l>I, a sinner, perplexed about the way I am agitated.</l>
<l>Where shall I meet now the father who extended</l>
<l>over the whole world, the one who guarded the cow herd that day with affection.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
